  <prompt>Update briefingService.ts to call the new /api/ai/daily-briefing/narrate endpoint instead of /summarize. Build the request from ChannelFetchResult[] — include full item data (id, title, body, priority, regardingName, regardingEntityType, regardingId, createdOn) per channel. Parse the NarrateResponse into TldrResult + ChannelNarrationResult[]. Create useBriefingNarration.ts hook that replaces useAiBriefing — returns { tldr, channelNarratives, isLoading, error }. Falls back to template-based generation when AI returns errors. Add Fluent Toaster provider and useToastController for toast notifications (used by inline To Do creation).</prompt>
